title: Liverpool may finally be celebrating a Premier League win in 2017 – but in reality their season is already over, says Alan Shearer
text:
EFL THE NEARLY MEN Liverpool may finally be celebrating a Premier League win in 2017 – but in reality their season is already over, says Alan Shearer 
A quick look at the league table and they are just in a battle to finish in the top four, a mile away from making a title challenge by ALAN SHEARER
